article_title: Life Without Private Equity, the Comic Strip Version
article_text:
“Carried Interest,” a comic strip focused on the quirky industry of leveraged buyouts, general partners and limited partners, is a regular feature in our monthly publication, Private Equity Analyst.

With Becky Pritchard’s recent exercise in self-denial in mind, here is the latest strip.
